{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act38side", "eventName": "揭幕者們", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "PV-1", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "失途", "storyInfo": "新沃爾西尼沒有家族，但家族從未放棄染指新城，他們以公司的名義，試圖滲透卡車工會。伊雷妮得知自己的好友正是在替威尼斯家族走私的途中撞傷了萊昂圖索。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "56_g9_truckcamp", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=2>1100年11月6日    1:35 P.M.</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_only_medium", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我讓彼得羅他們都出去了，營地暫時不會有人過來。", "name": "伊雷妮"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊雷妮，你昨天晚上不是和拉維妮婭法官在一起嗎？你知道萊昂圖索先生的傷勢怎麼樣嗎？他……他還活著嗎？", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨晚他好像已經搶救過來了，但……情況很不樂觀。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#7$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_chairrub", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#12$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-15", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡車司機像洩了氣的皮球般癱坐在椅子上，用滿是污漬的手套摀住了臉。"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他還這麼年輕，又是個好人……千萬不能——唉，我真是……！", "name": "索默爾"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底怎麼回事？", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是意外嗎？", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我也說不上來……我本來開得好好的，結果方向盤突然就不聽使喚了……", "name": "索默爾"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我根本來不及反應，整輛車直接失控，我當場撞暈了過去。等醒過來的時候，一切都已經發生了……", "name": "索默爾"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可……就算當時慌了手腳，你也不該把重傷的人丟在路邊不管啊！", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知不知道如果當時再耽誤一點搶救時間，萊昂圖索先生現在可能已經……", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "索默爾，你明明不是這樣的人。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起，伊雷妮……我真的想要救他的，我知道我應該救他，我不是沒種的壞人！", "name": "索默爾"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但、但我必須馬上把車開走。", "name": "索默爾"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼？", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#5$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "索默爾"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "索默爾，你別不說話啊。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#9$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "車上……有什麼東西嗎？", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#5$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊雷妮的聲音開始顫抖，癱坐在椅子上的司機臉色慘白。"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_chairrub", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1", "posfrom": "0,-30", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊雷妮……對不起……", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "索默爾，你到底在替誰開車？", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "威尼斯載具公司……威尼斯家族。", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "空氣陷入了漫長的沉默。不知道過了多久，伊雷妮才緩緩開口。"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是因為小古莉的事嗎？", "name": "伊雷妮"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊雷妮，不用幫我找藉口……我知道自己犯了多大的錯。", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#12$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼、為什麼寧願去找他們，也不願意向互助會尋求幫助呢？", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你明明是互助會資歷最深的司機，你很清楚我們在新沃爾西尼的地位有多特殊，市政廳和家族都在盯著我們的一舉一動。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊雷妮，治療礦石病的藥有多貴，你我都清楚。", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更別說把小古莉接來新沃爾西尼之後，還得安頓她，供她上個好一點的學校，這些開支根本不是普通人能負擔的……", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有我，索默爾。當初在西西里城，是你給了我一條活路。小古莉也是我的妹妹，你為什麼不告訴我？", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#7$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊雷妮，這根本不是互助會能幫我解決的。", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你就一個人……", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#7$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不對。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#5$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管是接駁從其他城市送到港口的物資，還是城內商戶之間的貨物轉運，我們經手的所有東西都必須事先登記。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#5$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這半年來，每一次排班表我都親自確認過，定期檢查也從未出過紕漏。你一個人怎麼可能辦得到，難道說——", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#5$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊雷妮，不只我一個人。", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#12$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g10_smallrestaurant", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1561_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……所以你們幾個也不知道索默爾去了哪裡。", "name": "家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1561_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他會不會已經連夜逃回西西里城了？畢竟撞了代理市長這麼大的事……", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1561_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "警察肯定會查到底的。我們會不會也被牽扯出來？偷運違禁品可是市政廳的紅線，況且我們還是在幫你們……", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1561_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不不，這件事和威尼斯載具公司可沒有任何關係。", "name": "家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "80,0", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1561_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1561_1#3$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼意思，你不會是想殺了我們滅口吧……", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1561_1#3$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "滅口？哈哈哈，我已經好久沒聽過這個詞了。", "name": "家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "w"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "w", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "80,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放輕鬆，別這麼緊張。你看，我手上現在有拿武器嗎？我只是希望你們不要說不該說的話，就這麼簡單。", "name": "家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1561_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可萬一警察真查到我們頭上怎麼辦？", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1561_1#3$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們一直瞞著伊雷妮，還頂著市政廳的壓力幫你們，如果事情真的鬧大了，你們不能光想着撇清關係！", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1561_1#3$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（聳肩）", "name": "家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真要深究的話，我們比你們還無辜呢。", "name": "家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "威尼斯載具公司從未違反《新都市管理法案》，也從未試圖滲透卡車工會，更沒有插手新沃爾西尼的物流系統。", "name": "家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1561_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什、什麼意思？", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1561_1#3$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "索默爾想把他女兒接來治療礦石病，對吧？", "name": "家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他找好了醫院，卻付不起治療費，所以隔三差五就用工會的卡車當醫院的私家運輸車，幫後勤部運貨。", "name": "家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那家醫院的資助企業裡，威尼斯載具公司排在最後一名。除了都在新沃爾西尼，我們和索默爾根本扯不上任何關係。", "name": "家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1561_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是這樣的……", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1561_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有你，一個酒精成癮者，每個月有一半時間連坐在駕駛座上都困難，為了不丟掉工作，偷偷找人代駕。", "name": "家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們可是簽了正式的委託協議的，我只不過是個想賺點外快的代駕員而已。", "name": "家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1561_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我那是生了病，不得不用來止痛……", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1561_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被你們找上的司機，哪個不是被你們抓住了把柄——", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1561_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新沃爾西尼可是個講法律的城市。我們大可以站上法庭，把證據一條條擺出來，到時候看看誰的屁股更乾淨。", "name": "家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1561_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們、你們這幫人，明明不拿刀，卻比拿著刀還可怕……", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1561_1#3$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？其實一開始，我還覺得自己這副模樣蠢得不行呢。", "name": "家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1561_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1561_1#3$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，放輕鬆點。", "name": "家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與其提心吊膽，不如幫我們追回那批“輪胎”，剩下的事情，我們會解決。", "name": "家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1554_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "56_g9_truckcamp", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#9$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……多久了？", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是半年前被他們找上的，在我之前，應該已經有幾十個司機跟他們接觸過了。", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#9$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒辦法……替他們跑一趟貨，拿到的錢比我們一個月薪水都要多。", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#9$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不配合的話，他們有的是辦法讓我們在這座城市活不下去。", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西西里夫人上台後，敘拉古各個城市的改革不計其數，那幫人適應遊戲規則的速度，比我們快太多了……", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是在為自己辯解，還是替其他人開脫？", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊雷妮……求求你，一定要幫幫我們！", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我向你保證！只要撐過這次狂歡節，我們就再也不幫那些人運貨了！", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以把我當作肇事者供出去，但一定要幫幫其他人，他們真的沒辦法才——", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……名單。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#11$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別想騙我，你們做這種事一定會留一份名單。交給我。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……至少得讓我知道你們有多少人牽扯其中，我才能去想辦法。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#11$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "索默爾放下了手裡緊握著的打火機，開始在身上翻找著什麼。"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#11$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "索默爾，你還留著這個打火機……我記得你不是早就戒菸了嗎？", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟是你送我的禮物，習慣帶在身上了。", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#9$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實這個東西是我當初在我們那家超市附近撿的，我哪有錢買這麼名貴的東西。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還記得嗎？小古莉的媽媽去世後，你接手了那家超市，一邊照顧她一邊打理生意。後來，有一天你在門口發現了無家可歸的我。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然你總說自己是撿了個“不用錢的進貨員兼店員”，但我知道，是你給了我容身之所，給了我一個家。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後來托科家族盯上了我們。那只是一個小家族，我們明明已經上架了他們的貨，他們還是不肯罷休，甚至威脅我們要把店裡所有同類商品都撤掉。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#7$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只是說“再商量商量”，結果當天夜裡，超市就被一場大火吞噬……小古莉也因此感染了礦石病……", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#7$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都是過去的事了，突然提這個幹嘛？", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#9$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找到了，給你。", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#9$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡米洛、吉安、魯傑羅……還真是讓人“驚喜”啊。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……對不起。", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#10$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別說那麼多了。索默爾，你去倉庫。那輛正在修的卡車後面有個木箱，幫我把它拿來。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那不是你存的……這根本是你的全部家當吧！", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#11$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好……好。", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#9$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "w"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "w", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#9$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-350,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_twohandedblunt", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punch02", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#9$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,-50", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#9$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#9$1", "posfrom": "-350,0", "posto": "-350,-15", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dragsofa", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "dr"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "dr", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#9$1", "posfrom": "-350,-15", "posto": "-200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$gavel1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_ironchaindrop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "索默爾，你不知道的是……這個打火機，就是我在那場火災的廢墟旁撿到的……", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們會來到新沃爾西尼，是因為我們已經一無所有了。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "索默爾……人都有糊塗的時候。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#3$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我不能讓你毀了這一切。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_vipward", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉維妮婭法官，您來了。", "name": "私人醫生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來看看萊昂。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有件事需要麻煩大家——希望萊昂的病情不要讓任何無關人士知曉。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請、請您放心，我能理解……", "name": "私人醫生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來沒有走錯地方。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請問你找誰？這裡是特殊病房，不能隨便靠近！", "name": "私人醫生"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，讓她進來吧。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "私人醫生"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉維妮婭法官，那我就先去忙了，您有事隨時叫我。", "name": "私人醫生"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……德克薩斯。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好久不見。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好久不見。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛才在樓下買了點千層酥跟通心粉，你隨便吃點，萊昂圖索這邊交給我看著。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我收到你們的邀請函了。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們一直沒等到回覆，還以為你這次不打算回新沃爾西尼了呢。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有點忙。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可頌拉著拜松在張羅什麼跨國新專案，空的敘拉古全境巡演才進行到一半，能天使更是不知道溜到哪裡去了……", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人手大減，但訂單一點沒少，最近企鵝物流的業務基本上都是我在處理。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說，這種人擠人的慶典真讓人提不起興趣，我還更希望哪天剛好接到個順路的委託再來看看你們。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那怎麼？", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰讓我有個愛湊熱鬧的老闆呢。有天晚上他碰巧看到了那封邀請函，轉頭就拉著我開始收拾行李。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他對你們辦的“主題派對”格外感興趣，直接推掉所有工作，甚至讓“大地的盡頭”停業半個月，硬是拉著我從龍門一路飛奔過來。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放輕鬆，拉維妮婭，你壓力太大了。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊昂他……", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經聽說了大概。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是意外？", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "警察還在調查。我剛從現場回來……可能性很低。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有懷疑的對象嗎？", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是那些人？", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "理由？", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照萊昂原本的計劃，狂歡節巡遊當晚，他會在全城的巡遊隊伍面前，正式宣布就任新沃爾西尼市長。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然這樣的決定不算稀奇，但他未免太著急了。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使他決定拋棄家族，他仍然是貝納爾多·貝洛內的兒子。一年的時間不足以讓人們遺忘貝納爾多曾在沃爾西尼掀起的驚濤駭浪。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隱身幕後，更能讓他順利推動新政府的運作，這才是最穩妥的做法。而不是換身衣服，放下防身的法杖，再次走到台前。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新沃爾西尼才剛建成一年，有西西里夫人的背書，他這個代理市長的位置也才勉強坐穩。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "delay": 0.4, "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "delay": 0.6, "channel": "BSE", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些話，我早就跟他說過了。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……也是。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "delay": 0.4, "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "delay": 0.6, "channel": "BSE", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉維妮婭，從剛剛開始，你腰上的通訊裝置就一直在閃。", "name": "德克薩斯"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "案子有新線索？", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是，是法院那邊的訊息，臨時有個案子……", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很棘手？", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "德克薩斯，我其實能理解為什麼萊昂這麼著急。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一年，新沃爾西尼的變化肉眼可見，許多曾經只存在於我們想像中的事，已經變成了現實。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這不正是西西里夫人所希望的嗎？", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是還不夠，遠遠不夠……所以我們必須彰顯自己的存在，才能推動更多的變革發生。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我也就沒有繼續勸他。結果……", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們還是跟以前一樣，不，比那時候更加天真，但這樣也不錯。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "德克薩斯，你要跟我一起去嗎？", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "法院？", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道的，我對人擠人的慶典不感興趣，對那些堆滿文件的公務更提不起勁。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我留在這裡負責萊昂的安全……目前應該沒有比我更合適的人了吧？", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，德克薩斯。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#9$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實如果你當時和我們一起留在新沃爾西尼——", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "德克薩斯", "content": "我說過，朋友出事，我就會來幫忙——"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "德克薩斯", "end": "true", "content": "我這不是來了嗎。", "joined": "我說過，朋友出事，我就會來幫忙——我這不是來了嗎。"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}